		<![CDATA[<b>Diana25:</b>	Hey, Emily. What are you doing tonight?

<b>Coolgirl:</b> Nothing much. Washing my hair, watching TV, listening to music. The usual. 

<b>Diana25:</b> That’s crazy. It’s Friday. The weather’s great and there’s a concert tonight in the park.   

<b>Coolgirl:</b> Hmm. Sounds good. What time’s the concert?

<b>Diana25:</b> 8:30. When do you want to meet?

<b>Coolgirl:</b> Let’s meet at 8:00, near the outdoor theater.

<b>Diana:</b> Great! See you there at 8:00.]]>
